    </Paragraph>
  </Subsection>

  <Subsection title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <Term type="command">check-configuration</Term> command validates configuration files.
    </Paragraph>

    <FormalItem title="Parameters">
      <xi:include href="LLCheckConfiguration.xml"/>
    </FormalItem>

    <Paragraph>
      The <Term type="command">check-configuration</Term> command will validate the configuration file specified with
      <Term type="parameter">--file</Term>.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
      If the command encounters no errors or warnings, it will not print anything.
    </Paragraph>
  </Subsection>

